The paper deals with the problem of exploring a graph using labels, which is a topic in graph theory and algorithms (cs.DS). The exploration is done by a mobile entity, which is a robot, and the paper proposes an algorithm for this task, which falls under robotics (cs.RO). The use of labels to guide the exploration involves some level of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the flexibility of adjusting the ratio of labels, which is related to optimization and decision-making (cs.SI).
